WEBVTT

00:01.968 --> 00:03.799
<i>Previously on</i> One Tree Hill.

00:03.870 --> 00:05.633
Hey, Mouth, have you seen Brooke?

00:05.705 --> 00:09.266
Yeah, she's benefiting with Felix.

00:10.377 --> 00:13.778
If my mom ever asks,
I got the test and I'm fine.

00:13.847 --> 00:15.144
If that's what you want.

00:15.215 --> 00:18.412
Yesterday,
Dan told me that you slept with Keith.

00:18.485 --> 00:21.147
-Is that true?
-No, of course not.

00:21.254 --> 00:24.655
I spent the whole night waiting for you,
all while you were with Chris.

00:24.724 --> 00:28.160
-Can we leave him out of this, please?
-Why? Are you into him?

00:28.228 --> 00:30.753
Just because people say something,
doesn't make it true, Felix.

00:31.164 --> 00:32.927
-Those were rumors.
-Yeah?

00:33.033 --> 00:35.228
How do you think rumors get started?

00:35.301 --> 00:38.168
It's okay,
I already flushed it down the toilet.

00:38.671 --> 00:40.298
I've only done it that one time.

00:40.373 --> 00:41.601
You don't get to have me...

00:41.674 --> 00:44.541
not my body,
and sure as hell not my heart.

00:44.644 --> 00:46.236
We're done.

00:46.646 --> 00:49.046
-We should do this more often.
-Do what?

00:50.016 --> 00:51.381
Be friends.

